body_text = "The [color=medium_blue]Tank[/color] is a class that focuses on taking hits from the enemy while reducing damage taken.

Their signature skill [color=medium_blue]Defend[/color] makes them take only [b]half[/b] the damage directed to them, making them extra [i]tanky[/i].

Consider pushing tanks into [color=firebrick]The Pit[/color] or quickly take out other units first.

